#: plugins/air_temp_humi/templates/air_temp_humi_help.html:8
msgid ""
"This plugin needs DHT11 (22) sensor connected to GPIO 10 (pin 19 MOSI). "
"Sensor DHT11 (22) is placed on main OSPy board by developer pihrt.com"
msgstr ""
"Tento doplnok potrebuje DHT11 alebo DHT22 senzor pripojený k GPIO 10 (pin 19 "
"MOSI). Senzor DHT11 alebo DHT22 je už umiestnený na hlavnej doske OSPy od "
"vývojára pihrt.com"

#: plugins/air_temp_humi/templates/air_temp_humi_help.html:9
msgid ""
"This plugin allows the control of some stations (eg Fan) depending on the "
"humidity of the sensor"
msgstr ""
"Tento plugin umožňuje ovládanie niektorých staníc (napr. Fan) v závislosti "
"na vlhkosti senzora"

#: plugins/air_temp_humi/templates/air_temp_humi_help.html:10
msgid ""
"This plug-in allows you to connect 1-6 DS18B20 sensors connected to the "
"external hardware board via an"
msgstr ""
"Tento doplnok umožňuje pripojiť 1-6 DS18B20 senzory pripojené k externej "
"hardvérovej doske cez"

#: plugins/air_temp_humi/templates/air_temp_humi_help.html:10
msgid "bus (address 0x03)"
msgstr "zbernicu I2C (adresa 0x03)"

