msgstr "Sťahovať JPEG obrázky"

#: plugins/ip_cam/templates/ip_cam_help.html:30
#: plugins/ip_cam/templates/ip_cam_setup.html:82
msgid ""
"When this option is checked, JPEG images will be downloaded after 5 seconds "
"to the plugin folder and these images will be previewed on the web page. "
"This option will make it possible to see preview images even from an "
"external IP address."
msgstr ""
"Keď je táto možnosť zaškrtnutá, obrázky JPEG sa stiahnu po 5 sekundách do "
"priečinka doplnku a tieto obrázky sa zobrazia na webovej stránke. Táto "
"možnosť umožní zobraziť náhľad obrázkov aj z externej IP adresy."

#: plugins/ip_cam/templates/ip_cam_help.html:31
#: plugins/ip_cam/templates/ip_cam_setup.html:89
msgid "Use GIF image creating"
msgstr "Vytvárať obrázky GIF"

#: plugins/ip_cam/templates/ip_cam_help.html:32
msgid ""
"When this option is checked, JPEG images will be downloaded after 5 seconds "
"(after 5 seconds an image is created - a gif animation is then created from "
"10 images) to the plugin folder and these images will be previewed on the "
"web page as GIF animation. This option will make it possible to see preview "
"images even from an external IP address."
msgstr ""
"Keď je táto možnosť zaškrtnutá, obrázky JPEG sa stiahnu po 5 sekundách (po 5 "
"sekundách sa vytvorí obrázok - z 10 obrázkov sa potom vytvorí animácia gif) "
"do priečinka doplnku a tieto obrázky sa na webovej stránke zobrazia ako "
"animácia GIF . Táto možnosť umožní zobraziť náhľad obrázkov aj z externej IP "
"adresy."

#: plugins/ip_cam/templates/ip_cam_help.html:33
#: plugins/ip_cam/templates/ip_cam_setup.html:97
msgid "Number of frames in GIF"
msgstr "Počet snímkov v GIFe"

#: plugins/ip_cam/templates/ip_cam_help.html:34
#: plugins/ip_cam/templates/ip_cam_setup.html:98
msgid ""
"How many images from the camera are saved and then used to create a GIF "
"image. (The more frames, the longer the gif will be refreshed. Frames are "
"created every 5 seconds. eg: 10 frames - gif is created in 10x5sec=50sec)."
msgstr ""
