"Including temperature sensors DS1 to DS6 from the temperature and humidity "
"monitor extension."
msgstr ""
"Vrátane teplotných senzorov DS1 až DS6 z rozšírenia o monitorovanie teploty "
"a vlhkosti."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant.html:220
msgid "Send errors"
msgstr "Chyby odosielania"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant.html:221
msgid ""
"If enabled, DS18B20 error values such as -127 are also sent to Home "
"Assistant."
msgstr ""
"Ak je povolený, DS18B20 chybové hodnoty ako -127 sa tiež odosielajú do Home "
"Assistant."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant.html:229
msgid "Extension: DHT"
msgstr "Rozšírenie: DHT"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant.html:230
msgid ""
"Including temperature/humidity sensors DHT from the temperature and humidity "
"monitor extension."
msgstr ""
"Vrátane senzorov teploty/vlhkosti DHT z rozšírenia monitora teploty a "
"vlhkosti."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant.html:238
msgid "Extension: sonic tank"
msgstr "Rozšírenie: sonický tank"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant.html:239
msgid "Including water level from the water tank (sonic) monitor extension."
msgstr "Vrátane predĺženia monitora vodnej nádrže (sonické)."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant.html:247
msgid "Extension: current loop tank"
msgstr "Predĺženie: nádrž s prúdovou slučkou"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant.html:248
msgid ""
"Including water level from the water tank (tanks with current loop) monitor "
"extension."
msgstr ""
"Vrátane predĺženia hladiny vody z vodnej nádrže (nádrže s prúdovým okruhom) "
"monitorovania hladiny."

