#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:3
#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:7
msgid "MQTT Home Assistant Plugin - help"
msgstr "Doplnok MQTT Home Assistant - pomocník"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:8
msgid "About the MQTT HASS Plugin"
msgstr "O doplnku MQTT HASS"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:10
msgid ""
"The MQTT HASS plugin implement MQTT Discovery for Home Assistant (HASS), "
"including report and control of some OSPy system settings and valves "
"(stations) over MQTT. MQTT Discovery enables automatic devices and entities "
"enrolment from HASS user interface configuration panel, including plug-and-"
"play availability detection, status and control."
msgstr ""
"Doplnok MQTT HASS implementuje MQTT Discovery pre Home Assistant (HASS), "
"vrátane správy a ovládania niektorých nastavení systému OSPy a ventilov "
"(staníc) cez MQTT. MQTT Discovery umožňuje automatickú registráciu zariadení "
"a entít z konfiguračného panela používateľského rozhrania HASS, vrátane "
"detekcie dostupnosti, stavu a riadenia plug-and-play."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:12
msgid "Using MQTT HASS plugin"
msgstr "Použiť doplnok MQTT Home Assistant"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:13
msgid ""
"This plugin is disabled by default. If you are reading this, the mqtt_hass "
"plugin is probably enabled on your system. Otherwise, you can enable it "
"using the plugin manager."
msgstr ""
"Tento doplnok je predvolene vypnutý. Ak toto čítate, doplnok mqtt_hass je "
"pravdepodobne vo vašom systéme povolený. V opačnom prípade ho môžete povoliť "
"pomocou správcu doplnkov."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:15
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Požiadavky"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:17
msgid ""
"An MQTT broker such as Mosquitto is required to be accessible by OSPy device "
"and HASS. This broker can be on different parts of the local network, on a "
"remote network, or installed on either OSPy or HASS system."
msgstr ""
"Sprostredkovateľ MQTT, ako je Mosquitto, musí byť prístupný pre zariadenie "
"OSPy a HASS. Tento sprostredkovateľ môže byť na rôznych častiach lokálnej "
"siete, na vzdialenej sieti, alebo môže byť nainštalovaný na systéme OSPy "
"alebo HASS."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:18
msgid "A working HASS system with an MQTT Integration such as Mosquitto broker"
msgstr ""
"Funkčný systém HASS s integráciou MQTT, ako je sprostredkovateľ Mosquitto"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:19
msgid ""
"A OSPy system with the base mqtt plugin installed and configured (see below)."
msgstr ""
"Systém OSPy s nainštalovaným a nakonfigurovaným základným doplnkom mqtt "
"(pozri nižšie)."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:20
msgid ""
"This plugin installed and configured on the same OSPy system as the base "
"mqtt plugin (see below)."
msgstr ""
"Tento doplnok je nainštalovaný a nakonfigurovaný na rovnakom systéme OSPy "
"ako základný doplnok mqtt (pozri nižšie)."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:25
msgid "On OSPy - base MQTT plugin setup"
msgstr "Na OSPy - základné nastavenie doplnku MQTT"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:27
msgid "Install eclipse paho if not already on the Pi"
msgstr "Nainštalujte eclipse paho, ak ešte nie je na Pi"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:28
msgid "Install the base MQTT plugin"
msgstr "Inštalácia základného doplnku MQTT"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:29
msgid "Configure base MQTT plugin"
msgstr "Konfigurácia  základného doplnku MQTT"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:31
msgid ""
"MQTT Broker Host: This will be the URL of the MQTT broker or localhost if "
"the broker is running on OSPy"
msgstr ""
"MQTT Broker Host: Toto bude adresa URL sprostredkovateľa MQTT alebo "
"localhost, ak sprostredkovateľ beží na OSPy"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:32
msgid ""
"MQTT Broker Port: Default is 1883 but may be different depending on your "
"MQTT broker"
msgstr ""
"Port sprostredkovateľa MQTT: Predvolená hodnota je 1883, ale môže sa líšiť v "
"závislosti od vášho sprostredkovateľa MQTT"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:33
msgid "MQTT Broker Username: Default is mosquitto but depends on your setup."
msgstr ""
"Používateľské meno sprostredkovateľa MQTT: Predvolené je mosquitto, ale "
"závisí od vášho nastavenia."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:34
msgid "MQTT Broker Password: Depends on your setup. Use pass as default"
msgstr ""
"Heslo sprostredkovateľa MQTT: Závisí od vášho nastavenia. Použiť heslo ako "
"predvolené"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:35
msgid ""
"MQTT Client ID: A unique name for OSPy system. Default is OSPy System name "
"but can be changed on Options webpage."
msgstr ""
"ID klienta MQTT: Jedinečný názov pre systém OSPy. Predvolený je názov "
"systému OSP."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:39
msgid "On OSPy - MQTT HASS plugin setup"
msgstr "Na OSPy - nastavenie MQTT HASS doplnku"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:41
msgid "Install Python python-slugify package if not already on the pi."
msgstr "Nainštalujte balík Python python-slugify, ak ešte nie je na pi."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:43
msgid "Configure MQTT HASS plugin."
msgstr "Nakonfigurujte doplnok MQTT HASS."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:45
msgid ""
"Topic prefix: This prefix is used for OSPy system parameters and zones "
"published to the MQTT broker. Leave this option empty to use a slugified "
"OSPy System name. This setting will be slugified when saved. (Default: "
"System name or \"OSPy\" if System name is empty)."
msgstr ""
"Predpona témy: Táto predpona sa používa pre systémové parametre a zóny OSPy "
"publikované do MQTT sprostredkovateľa. Ak chcete použiť zakomponovaný názov "
"systému OSPy, nechajte túto možnosť prázdnu. Toto nastavenie bude po uložení "
"zlúčené. (Predvolené: Názov systému alebo „OSPy“, ak je názov systému "
"prázdny)."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:46
msgid ""
"Name prefix: Used as prefix for all HASS devices and entities names. Leave "
"this option empty to use a OSPy System name as prefix. For entities, this "
"setting will be slugified. (Default: System name or \"OSPy\" if System name "
"is empty)."
msgstr ""
"Predpona názvu: Používa sa ako predpona pre všetky názvy zariadení a entít "
"HASS. Ak chcete ako predponu použiť názov systému OSPy, nechajte túto "
"možnosť prázdnu. Pre entity bude toto nastavenie skrátené. (Predvolené: "
"Názov systému alebo „OSPy“, ak je názov systému prázdny)."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:47
msgid ""
"OSPy FQDN: OSPy network name or IP address. Used to compose the URL link to "
"OSPy web interface displayed in HASS devices settings. Leave this option "
"empty to use OSPy hostname or IP address used to connect with the MQTT "
"broker. (Default: OSPy hostname)."
msgstr ""
"OSPy FQDN: Názov siete alebo IP adresa OSPy. Používa sa na vytvorenie odkazu "
"URL na webové rozhranie OSPy zobrazené v nastaveniach zariadení HASS. Ak "
"chcete použiť názov hostiteľa OSPy alebo adresu IP použitú na pripojenie k "
"sprostredkovateľovi MQTT, nechajte túto možnosť prázdnu. (Predvolené: názov "
"hostiteľa OSPy)."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:48
msgid ""
"Device is Station name: if checked, use station name as part of HASS Device "
"name. Changes to OSPy station name will update HASS Device name. (Default: "
"unchecked)"
msgstr ""
"Zariadenie je názov stanice: ak je začiarknuté, použite názov stanice ako "
"súčasť názvu zariadenia HASS. Zmeny názvu stanice OSPy aktualizujú názov "
"zariadenia HASS. (Predvolené: nezačiarknuté)"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:52
msgid "On Home Assistant - MQTT setup"
msgstr "Na Home Assistant - nastavenia MQTT"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:54
msgid ""
"Follow Home Assistant instructions to add MQTT integration via the user "
"interface. MQTT discovery feature is enabled by default. MQTT integration "
"will detect OSPy settings parameters and zones as devices and entities."
msgstr ""
"Postupujte podľa pokynov Home Assistant a pridajte integráciu MQTT cez "
"používateľské rozhranie. Funkcia zisťovania MQTT je predvolene povolená. "
"Integrácia MQTT zistí parametre a zóny nastavení OSPy ako zariadenia a "
"entity."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:55
msgid ""
"Follow Home Assistant instructions to configure and use the newly added "
"devices and entities."
msgstr ""
"Podľa pokynov Home Assistant nakonfigurujte a používajte novo pridané "
"zariadenia a entity."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:58
msgid ""
"Multiple OSPy systems connected to the same MQTT broker or Home Assistant "
"instance"
msgstr ""
"Viacero systémov OSPy pripojených k rovnakému sprostredkovateľovi MQTT alebo "
"inštancii Home Assistant"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:60
msgid "To integrate multiple OSPy systems, on each OSPy:"
msgstr "Ak chcete integrovať viacero systémov OSPy, na každom OSPy:"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:61
msgid ""
"Use different \"System name\" as set on OSPy Options webpage. Default OSPy "
"System name is \"OSPy\""
msgstr ""
"Použite iný \"Názov systému\", ako je nastavený na webovej stránke Možnosti "
"OSPy. Predvolený názov systému OSPy je \"OSPy\""

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:62
msgid "For each MQTT HASS plugin use different Topic prefix and Name prefix."
msgstr ""
"Pre každý doplnok MQTT HASS použite inú predponu témy a predponu názvu."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:65
msgid "Home Assistant - available OSPy Devices and Entities"
msgstr "Home Assistant – dostupné OSPy zariadenia a entity"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:66
msgid "Devices and associated Entities made available with this plugin are:"
msgstr "Zariadenia a súvisiace entity sprístupnené s týmto doplnkom sú:"

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:68
msgid ""
"System device: rain delay control, water level adjustment, scheduler enable "
"switch, manual operation switch, and rain sensor state."
msgstr ""
"Systémové zariadenie: ovládanie oneskorenia dažďa, nastavenie hladiny vody, "
"prepínač aktivácie plánovača, manuálny spínač a stav dažďového senzora."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:69
msgid ""
"Station devices: one switch entity for each enabled OSPy station, allowing "
"the station to be switched on or off from Home Assistant."
msgstr ""
"Zariadenia stanice: jedna prepínacia entita pre každú povolenú OSPy stanicu, "
"ktorá umožňuje zapnúť alebo vypnúť stanicu z Home Assistant."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:70
msgid ""
"Program devices: one button entity for each OSPy program, allowing the "
"program to be started from Home Assistant."
msgstr ""
"Programové zariadenia: jedna jednotka tlačidla pre každý OSPy program, ktorá "
"umožňuje spustiť program z Home Assistant."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:71
msgid ""
"Stop buttons: button entities for stopping all stations from the station and "
"program device groups."
msgstr ""
"Tlačidlá na zastavenie: entity na zastavenie všetkých staníc zo stanice a "
"programovanie skupín zariadení."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:72
msgid ""
"Temperature and humidity extension entities, when enabled: DHT temperature, "
"DHT humidity, and DS1 to DS6 temperature sensors from the air temperature "
"and humidity plugin."
msgstr ""
"Entity na rozšírenie teploty a vlhkosti, keď sú zapnuté: DHT teplota, DHT "
"vlhkosť a senzory teploty DS1 na DS6 z pluginu pre teplotu a vlhkosť vzduchu."

#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:73
msgid ""
"DS18B20 error filtering, when enabled in settings: DS error values such as "
"-127 can be sent or suppressed before publishing to Home Assistant."
msgstr ""
