#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:3
#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:7
msgid "Shelly Cloud Integration - help"
msgstr "Shelly Cloud Integration - pomocník"

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:8
msgid ""
"This extension adds integration of Shelly devices into the OSPy ecosystem. "
"After setting up this extension and adding devices, these devices will "
"appear in OSPy sensors and you will be able to work with them further."
msgstr ""
"Tento doplnok pridáva integráciu zariadení Shelly do ekosystému OSPy. Po "
"nastavení tohto doplnku a pridaní zariadení sa tieto zariadenia zobrazia v "
"senzoroch OSPy a budete s nimi môcť ďalej pracovať."

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:9
msgid "How to get the latest device status via Shelly Cloud API and curl."
msgstr "Ako získať najnovší stav zariadenia cez Shelly Cloud API a Curl."

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:10
msgid "Path: https:// <***server_uri > /device/status."
msgstr "Cesta: https:// <***server_uri > /device/status."

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:11
msgid "Supported methods: GET and POST."
msgstr "Podporované metódy: GET a POST."

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:12
msgid "Parameters are supplied via *query or **request body"
msgstr ""
"Parametre sa poskytujú prostredníctvom  *query alebo **textu požiadavkyt"

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:13
msgid "Required data to send the request:"
msgstr "Požadované údaje pre odoslanie žiadosti:"

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:14
msgid "Target device ID: key = \"id\""
msgstr "ID cieľového zariadenia: key = \"id\""

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:15
msgid " **** account authentication key: key = \"auth_key\""
msgstr " Overovací kľúč účtu: Key = \"auth_key\""

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:16
msgid "The result is a JSON object with the device status."
msgstr "Výsledkom je objekt JSON so stavom zariadenia."

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:17
msgid ""
"The server URL where all the devices and client accounts are located. This "
"can be obtained from Shelly > User Settings > Cloud Authorization Key."
msgstr ""
"URL adresa servera, kde sa nachádzajú všetky zariadenia a klientske účty. "
"Túto adresu je možné získať v časti Shelly > Nastavenia používateľa > "
"Autorizačný kľúč cloudu."

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:18
msgid "Shelly API"
msgstr "Shelly API"

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:21
msgid "Reading data over the local network"
msgstr "Čítanie dát cez lokálnu sieť"

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:22
msgid ""
"From devices that are permanently connected to the local network (Wi-Fi or "
"LAN), data can be read directly outside the Shelly cloud. The advantage is "
"that data can be read regardless of the cloud provider, i.e. Shelly cloud "
"API. This method cannot be used for devices that sleep and wake up (for "
"example shelly H&T, etc.) and are not permanently connected to the network."
msgstr ""
"Zo zariadení, ktoré sú trvalo pripojené k lokálnej sieti (Wi-Fi alebo LAN), "
"je možné čítať dáta priamo mimo cloudu Shelly. Výhodou je, že dáta je možné "
"čítať bez ohľadu na poskytovateľa cloudu, t. j. cloudové API Shelly. Túto "
"metódu nemožno použiť pre zariadenia, ktoré spia a prebúdzajú sa (napríklad "
"Shelly H&T atď.) a nie sú trvalo pripojené k sieti."

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:23
msgid ""
"In the device settings (for devices that support it) there is an option to "
"select reading: cloud or locally."
msgstr ""
"V nastaveniach zariadenia (pre zariadenia, ktoré to podporujú) je možnosť "
"vybrať si čítanie: cloud alebo lokálne."

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:24
msgid ""
"Example of reading data over the local network for a gen1 device. http://IP/"
"status"
msgstr ""
"Príklad čítania údajov cez lokálnu sieť pre zariadenie gen1. http://IP/status"

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:25
msgid ""
"Example of reading data over the local network for a gen2+ device. http://IP/"
"rpc/Shelly.GetStatus"
msgstr ""
"Príklad čítania údajov cez lokálnu sieť pre zariadenie gen2+. http://IP/rpc/"
"Shelly.GetStatus"

#: plugins/shelly_cloud_integrator/templates/shelly_cloud_integration_help.html:26
msgid ""
"If you do not want to use the cloud, but only the local network, fill in at "
"least 5 arbitrary characters. Some devices are not available on the local "
"network (e.g. Wi-FI H&T)."
msgstr ""
"Ak nechcete používať cloud, ale iba lokálnu sieť, vyplňte aspoň 5 "
"ľubovoľných znakov. Niektoré zariadenia nie sú v lokálnej sieti dostupné "
"(napr. Wi-Fi H&T)."

