#: plugins/sunrise_and_sunset/templates/sunrise_and_sunset_setup.html:79
msgid ""
"If the program does not have a days marked, it will not start (neither by "
"the \"run now\" button in the programs, nor by this plug-in)!"
msgstr ""
"Ak program nemá označené dni, nespustí sa (ani tlačidlom \"spustiť teraz\" v "
"programoch, ani týmto doplnkom)!"

#: plugins/sunrise_and_sunset/templates/sunrise_and_sunset_setup.html:85
