"zastavuje vybrané programy OSPy, keď sú dosiahnuté nastavené teplotné limity."

#: plugins/thermostat/templates/thermostat_help.html:9
msgid ""
"Use low and high temperature values with one decimal place to create "
"hysteresis. For example, low 22.4 C and high 22.6 C means that no action is "
"repeated while the temperature stays between these values."
