"Do adresára skladieb môžete nahrať ľubovoľnú skladbu s ľubovoľným názvom vo "
"formáte mp3 a wav."

#: plugins/voice_notification/templates/voice_notification_help.html:12
msgid ""
"Unlike the \"voice station\" package, this extension has a connection to the "
"program scheduler (ie how the programs and stations assigned in them are set "
"up.) In this extension, the song is played some time before the program "
"starts..."
