#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor.html:329
msgid ""
"The measured data will be stored in the database. This option requires the "
"database connector extension to be installed and configured. The button will "
"delete the windmonitor table from the database, thus deleting all saved data "
"from this extension! This promotion is non-refundable!"
